  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Sauté garlic and leek until softened.",
    "Add Tom Yum paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add pork, fish sauce, and lime juice, and stir to combine.",
    "Add coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add bell peppers and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in Thai basil and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Serve soup with crusty bread and tempering chocolate on the side, if using."
  ],
